Lifting State Up:-Lifting State Up → jab 2–3 close components ko same state chahiye Lifting State Up ka matlab state ko child se utha kar common parent me rakhna, taaki multiple components same state use kar sakein.

Parent
 ├─ Child1
 └─ Child2


Example :-
function Parent() {
  const [name, setName] = useState("");

  return (
    <>
      <Child1 name={name} setName={setName} />
      <Child2 name={name} />
    </>
  );
}
